data.description: Location and Energy efficiency at its best!  Recently installed Solar Panels and high end water softener convey with they house... $40k worth of extras, yours at no cost!!!       Welcome to this exceptional home where comfort meets sustainability. Situated in a sought-after community of Talise de Culebra, in the Alamo Ranch area, this 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom gem boasts a plethora of features and amenities.    Key Highlights:  Sustainable Living: Recently installed solar panels convey with the sale, ensuring virtually zero electricity bills. Experience significant monthly savings without lifting a finger, as the seller will pay off the solar panels at closing.    Water Quality: Indulge in the softest water, thanks to the top-tier water softener system that will also convey with the home.    Master Suite Downstairs: Retreat to your main-floor master bedroom oasis complete with a double vanity, spacious master closet, and both tub & shower.    Open Living: Revel in the expansive open floorplan, making family gatherings and entertaining a breeze. Step outside to a generous backyard, perfect for alfresco dining or your next garden project.    Tax Savings: An added bonus - this home does not pay city taxes!    Community Perks: Dive into the resort-style swimming pool on hot summer days or partake in various activities at the community center. The neighborhood also offers scenic walking trails and a basketball court for outdoor enthusiasts.    Unbeatable Location: Centrally positioned, this home offers easy access to shopping, dining, entertainment, and major highways. Plus, with proximity to employers like Lackland AFB and Microsoft, and attractions like Sea World and Fiesta Texas, weekend plans are sorted.
